Gelish Top It Off Gel is a sealer top gel designed to create the ultimate finish with your Gelish Soak Off Polish. It creates a high shine that will not dull, chip or peel. Top It Off is a soak off product that can quickly be removed with Soak Off Gel Remover. This coat cures in 30 seconds in a LED Light or 2 minutes in a UV Light.

title: Gelish A MINT OF SPRING Love in Bloom Collection Gel Nail Polish .5 oz Harmony
description:
Harmony Gelish Soak-Off Gel Polish

Love in Bloom Collection - A MINT OF SPRING

From Harmony's new Gelish Spring time collection, Love in Bloom, comes a series of vibrant and bold polishes inspired by the colors of Spring. Harmony's luxurious Gel polish will stay intact and chip free for up to 3 weeks. Gelish nail polish applies easily like standard nail polish with a twist off cap applicator, but must be cured under a UV or LED lamp. This gorgeous professional polish only takes minutes to apply and will last you all through Spring!

About Gel Nail Polish:

    Easy Application
    Stay on for up to 3 weeks
    Cures in as fast as 30 seconds
    Perfect for a Do-It-Yourself Mani or Pedi

Application and Removal:

Apply the polish over Gelish foundation or structure Gel. Never apply directly to the natural nail! Gel nail Polish is heat activated and must be cured under a LED light or UV light system. Gelish nail polish becomes cured in only 30 seconds under a LED lamp, or approximately 2 minutes under a traditional UV lamp. Gelish polish stays on nails for approximately 3 weeks with no chipping or peeling! when you are ready to remove Gelish polish, soak for 15 minutes.
